{
  "chapter": 33,
  "chapter_summary": "芮玮与林琼菊来到点苍山顶一处蓝瓦院落，遇到两名尼姑打扮的妙龄女子紫凤和玉凤，实为蓝髯客路庭花的弟子。蓝衫大汉路庭花现身，与芮玮交手，掌法精妙令海渊剑法五剑均无法取胜，芮玮被打两记耳光。路庭花欲收林琼菊为弟子，削断其长发相逼，芮玮无奈答应学习化神掌换取林琼菊自由。芮玮以飞龙八步施展奇步，抢回林琼菊。路庭花透露其真实身份，强迫芮玮学习化神掌七日。芮玮学成后感激传艺之恩，路庭花嘱其不得对外人提及此事。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恐怕不是一灯神尼的住处，咱们又找错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不会吧，点苍山顶终年积雪，谁会在这里盖这么一大栋的屋宇，八成是神尼修行的地方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "一定不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nun_greeting",
      "speaker_name": "妙龄尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "何方贵客驾临敝处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "还是菊妹说对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下芮玮求见一灯神尼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "原来是芮公子，久仰公子大名，怎么来到咱们这儿？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "玉凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "公子长得好俊，到咱们屋里喝盏茶再走吧？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "谁要喝你们的茶，咱们要见神尼，不是来喝茶的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "哎哟，好凶！我说芮公子她是您的什么人？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "请向令师传禀一声，芮玮求见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "玉凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要见咱们的师父？正好，他老人家也要见你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_feng",
      "text": "就请传见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可是话要说在前头，我们的师父不是尼姑呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "那你们也不是尼姑啦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "本来嘛，我们哪里是尼姑呀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yu_feng",
      "text": "不是尼姑，两位一定是名门千金啦？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "玉凤",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "谈不上名门，家父只是个知府罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "那你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "请芮公子猜猜看？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "谁有兴致来猜，快带咱们求见神尼。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不忙，咱们再聊一会，等下见到师父，你们就要走了，那时想聊也没机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "紫凤、玉凤，叫你们看是谁来，怎么聊起天了？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好小子，敢对我无礼，站住！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "无礼便又怎样？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "小子，你早该拔剑啦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不行，不行，快使海渊剑法。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "怎么不斗了，莫非自知打不过吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "你掌法精妙，我不是你的对手，我对你无礼任凭处置！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你去罢，你承认输了，就得了，还处置什么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "咱们走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那丫头说海渊八剑天下无敌，简直骗人！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "海渊八剑确是天下无敌的剑法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要是天下无敌的剑法，你为何使到第五剑便自知不敌，不敢再使了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "那两剑我没学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "去求见一灯神尼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你八剑未学会，还去见她做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "在下此来点苍山，势在必见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "张丫头和你说什么来着？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "一灯神尼传言说：若未学会八剑来点苍山见她，必然对在下不利。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "岂止不利，我劝你不要去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "多谢相劝，我命一条，难道一灯神尼会要了我的命。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "你这是什么意思？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放开我！放开我……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你去送死，可别叫她陪你送死。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要你管，快放开我！大哥，大哥，来救我啊！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "你究是何种用意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我要救她一命，你不愿意吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "我带她去自有不使她受伤害之法，请你放下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你连我也斗不过，别想打得过张丫头，自身难保，还谈什么不使她受害，要知张丫头杀起人来，可厉害呢！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你还不救我，打他一顿……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "你到底放不放她？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不放，不放，喂，我说小丫头你哭什么，跟我做名弟子吧？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "谁要做你的弟子，你再不放下我，我要咬你了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "别人想跟我做弟子，我还不要，我看中你，是你的造化……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咬呀！咬呀！用劲咬呀，老夫有个怪脾气，你越是不想做我的弟子，我就非要你做不可，今天徒弟收定啦！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你敢再动？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你想在我手中夺她，如同白日做梦，势如登天。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "天下哪有强迫人家做弟子的道理？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "当然有这道理。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "敢情你的弟子全要强迫人家做的！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "胡说八道……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "以在下看来，你的弟子莫非全是抢来的，令得人家不做也不成？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "紫风、玉风过来！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你们跟这小子说，可是我要你们做弟子来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁要强迫我啊，我就是死也不愿意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "玉凤",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我说姑娘，你就拜我们师父做名弟子吧，他老人家本领可大呢，你想学什么，他老人家就能教你什么。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_yu_feng",
      "text": "谁像你们不要脸，出了家还不清净。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "谁不要脸啦？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "我说你们不要脸，尼姑庵还能留男人住吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "丫头别弄错了，这里不是尼姑庵。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "不是尼姑庵怎会住着尼姑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "玉凤",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "跟你说过咱们不是尼姑，怎么又乱说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "凡我弟子皆是尼姑打扮，小丫头，你要做我弟子也是尼姑打扮。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "谁要做你的弟子，放开我，放开我。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹别闹，这位前辈是个讲理的人，他的弟子都是情愿的，你不愿意，他定会放你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "今天说什么也要这丫头做我的弟子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好步法！你会这套步法足可保住小丫头不受害，当可带她去见张丫头，我先前倒是杞人忧天啦。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "姓芮的，你那套步法跟谁学的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，这人坏死啦，别理他。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你那步法可是红袍公任有庆传授的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "什么红袍公我不认识，那套步法是我家传绝学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别要骗我，既然红袍公传你一套步法，我也来传你一套绝学吧？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "多谢美意，在下不愿学。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要学，我要传你适才海渊五剑无法击败的化神掌法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这人掌法虽好，品格太坏，他的掌法大哥不要学。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不学也罢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你学不学？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "大哥就是不要跟他学！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "要你这丫头多什么嘴！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "紫凤接着！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "这次你别妄想再救，紫风，把那丫头关起来，饿她几天几夜，看她还有精神说话不？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 425
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "慢着，你们不能关她。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不关可以，但你得乖乖地将化神掌法学会。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "天下还有强迫学艺的道理吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "跟你说过，老夫有个怪癖，越是不要跟老夫学艺，老夫却一定要他学。紫风听着，这姓芮的一天不跟我学化神掌法，便一天不给那丫头饭吃，还要好好打她一顿。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "紫凤",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "是，师父。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "你们不要关她，在下跟你们师父学那化神掌就是。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要学，咱们现在就开始。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你安心与那两位姐姐住在屋内，大哥学会化神掌即接你出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_feng",
      "speaker_name": "玉凤",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "芮公子，你放心，咱们这里姐姐可多着呢，保证不会亏待她。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "今天你可以去见张丫头了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "前辈费尽心血将化神掌相传，后辈感激不尽。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 469
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不要感激我，我传你化神掌自有用意，说来还是为我自己，你要感激我，那就吃亏。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "text": "不论前辈有何用意，既以高深武学相传，晚辈再也不会忘记传艺之恩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 477
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "但你别忘了，你本来不愿学，是我强迫你学的呢。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你要感激我也无法阻止，可是有一点你要记住，这化神掌相传之事不准向别人提及，亦不准说曾见过我！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "路庭花",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "数日相处，总不能连我是谁你也不知，临别在即，我不妨告诉你，我姓路名庭花，人称蓝髯客。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 493
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_zi_feng",
      "text": "将林姑娘带出来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_ran_ke",
      "speaker_name": "蓝衫大汉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好啦，该让他们走了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 33,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    }
  ],
